Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.41,0:01:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片名:砂制时镜下的疗养院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.04,0:04:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎样找到它呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己会找到路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.95,0:08:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走了很长的一段路\N在这儿预订了房间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都睡着了\N晚一会儿,我告诉医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但暂时还没到夜间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们一直睡在这里,你不知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外,这里从来没有夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好在楼下等着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在餐馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,医生现在要见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.75,0:11:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在哪儿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们昨天接到了你的电报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.08,0:11:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们派马车去火车站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,你一定是坐\N另一趟火车过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到火车站?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸的是,那列火车的服务不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我父亲活着吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.29,0:11:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是在那种范围之内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.79,0:11:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被形势所强加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:12:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了你的祖国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和为了你们国家的信念...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都知道这是不能被完全治愈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的死,在这里的他的\N存在上面投下了某种阴影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.25,0:12:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他不知道或猜不到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别着急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的病人不要怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.75,0:12:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在可能想去看看他,我带你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.87,0:13:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你父亲的房间里\N我们为你预留了一张床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照你的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.41,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整件蠢事就是:\N我们把钟放了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.00,0:13:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每隔一定的时间就放回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.87,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个时间,我们是不能精确地限定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.37,0:14:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整件事是一个相互依存的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.20,0:14:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这儿,你父亲的死依然会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你们国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那同一个死神已经杀了他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是说,我爸爸是死了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.83,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是将要死呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这儿,我们以所有的\N可能性使时间恢复流动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括让时间重新来过的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们允许病人们长时间的睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是为了节省他们\N维持生命所必需的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外,他们别无选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也该躺下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.75,0:15:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你的当务之急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我过来跟你谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你散布关于父亲的\N所有谎言和流言蜚语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.20,0:19:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么意图呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 什么谎言?\N- 我知道是你散布的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.45,0:20:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我没有说谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你记得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.45,0:20:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已经失踪好多天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他避开了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.62,0:20:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且,谁知他是否仍在某处活着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.79,0:20:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.58,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别再烦我,你知道\N现在和他说话有多难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么能够独自处理所有的事情呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎么能够回答...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.70,0:20:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上帝一直问我的所有问题呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它超出了我的忍耐力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他疾病的严重性让我很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.04,0:20:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 别哭了\N- 我偏头疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今天别去学校了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.83,0:20:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去学校,妈妈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不再是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.37,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是的,你是小孩子\N看看你那沾满墨水的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有你那青肿的膝盖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是个淘气、固执的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上帝知道你在哪游荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去叫醒那帮无用的人,那帮寄生虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,商店应该马上开门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 但是...\N- 别再烦我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.45,0:21:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我经常跟你说\N你爸爸作为一名推销员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.25,0:21:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,周游全国各地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.16,0:21:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道,他有时夜里回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.95,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是为了在黎明前能走得更远些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我确信他会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.70,0:22:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别翻来覆去的了,坐起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.83,0:23:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 打一小会儿哈欠...\N- 再休息一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你休息完了之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.33,0:23:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就去蚂蚁屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.79,0:23:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去学习知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.66,0:23:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学蚂蚁?去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的那只蚂蚁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.58,0:23:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有老师、主人或老板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.08,0:23:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但她是富有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在说什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.37,0:23:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.29,0:23:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个懒惰男人的田地里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.12,0:23:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正穿过...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个愚蠢男人的葡萄园...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.95,0:23:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪儿都没写这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的上帝从未说过它。别听它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.95,0:23:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的土地上是:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.66,0:23:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荨麻丛生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.79,0:23:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荆棘遍布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.04,0:24:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,断壁残垣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.58,0:24:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<i>拍拍你的手</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.37,0:24:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<i>呼唤他的名</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.91,0:24:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<i>用愉快的声音</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.25,0:24:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<i>用幸福的赞歌\N呼唤他的名</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.16,0:24:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<i>伴随小号的奏鸣</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.29,0:24:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,<i>为你的赞美伴奏</i>
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.50,0:25:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用竖琴赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.91,0:25:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用齐特琴赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.50,0:25:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用鼓和舞蹈赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.08,0:25:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用琴弦和长笛赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.83,0:25:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用铙钹悦耳的音调赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.79,0:25:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用铙钹响亮地赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.08,0:26:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让每一位神灵赞美他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.04,0:26:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿利路亚!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.08,0:26:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拍手唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.50,0:26:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.04,0:26:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为那些可怜的灵魂唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.20,0:26:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在梦里,他看到一架梯子立在地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.45,0:26:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梯子的顶端直达天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.70,0:26:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上帝的天使们正攀上攀下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.12,0:27:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可能吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.95,0:27:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的小约瑟夫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.83,0:27:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可能在去往学校的途中迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.12,0:27:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀... 淘气鬼! 他们无处不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:55.12,0:27:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我清早要下去买面包时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:58.91,0:28:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我甚至不能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.58,0:28:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.75,0:28:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们从这些最小的豁口蜂拥而入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.70,0:28:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们试图进到厨房里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.08,0:28:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们勾引我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.66,0:28:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们几乎摇尾乞怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:33.29,0:28:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当他们看到一堆火时,他们发疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.33,0:28:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们像野蛮人一样拍手跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.04,0:28:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们没有办法去灭火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.87,0:28:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有游行时,他们才派得上用场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.45,0:28:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在谈论谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.75,0:28:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些无所事事的消防员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.83,0:28:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋末,他们变得慵懒和昏昏欲睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.37,0:28:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们可以站着睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.58,0:28:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你是怀有偏见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.08,0:29:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是不错的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.37,0:29:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个老火炉匠曾告诉我\N在他修理烟囱时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.08,0:29:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他发现他们依附在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.00,0:29:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通风口上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.95,0:29:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像幼虫一样不动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:30.75,0:29:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们睡在那儿,因喝树莓酒而醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.54,0:29:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且哀求地叫着:\N“宝贝,宝贝”...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.91,0:29:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只需瞥他们一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:47.91,0:29:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们脸就立刻红胀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.75,0:29:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带着那种淫秽的暗红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:55.95,0:29:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通过那种方式,他们增强内心的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.79,0:30:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且复原色彩:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.75,0:30:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样,消防员扑灭例如:烟火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.00,0:30:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭和孟加拉大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.83,0:30:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会随便给他们任何甜酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.95,0:30:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能在火炉上做饭\N那样会毁坏我的肤色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:14.33,0:30:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恰好现在那帮流氓可以全喝了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.58,0:30:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸的是,阿德拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.12,0:30:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从未理解那些超越世俗的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.12,0:30:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.75,0:30:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把头发蓄到地面那么长是可能的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.33,0:30:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看上去完全不同了,太好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.08,0:30:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那帮流氓的队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:53.12,0:30:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“我,安娜·克希莱,在莫拉维亚出生\N头发稀疏...”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.83,0:30:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望我的也能像她的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.08,0:31:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要来点儿甜酒吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.54,0:31:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 要树莓酒吗?\N- 不,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.12,0:31:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.08,0:31:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由神授意,使她的头发稀疏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.95,0:31:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但通过虔诚的祷告和苦修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.41,0:31:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她头上的诅咒消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.12,0:31:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通过教化她变得美丽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.04,0:31:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她得到了神迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:30.58,0:31:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调制了那种神奇的秘方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.41,0:31:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:38.54,0:31:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是那些兄弟们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.12,0:31:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲戚和朋友们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.37,0:31:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是谁啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.58,0:31:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个朋友,她把幸福带给全体镇民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.16,0:31:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.70,0:32:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“艾尔莎,流体和天鹅在一起”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.08,0:32:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是一种神奇的秘方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.70,0:32:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以包治百病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.37,0:32:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪儿找到的这本书?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.79,0:32:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它一直在这儿的\N就放在附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.04,0:32:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“你随便吸烟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.95,0:32:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性欲恐惧症”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.54,0:32:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天我们都撕下几页用来包肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.12,0:32:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是给你父亲的午餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:42.04,0:32:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神圣原始资料的如此堕落!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.70,0:33:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来晚了,没有更多甜酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.62,0:33:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有些玫瑰花蜜饯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.83,0:33:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己动手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.50,0:33:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.95,0:33:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是蜜饯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.75,0:33:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但它也是甜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.45,0:33:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫贾科布?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.62,0:33:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我叫约瑟夫\N我父亲叫贾科布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.62,0:33:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.83,0:33:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以出来吗?\N我们不能像这样谈话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.70,0:33:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 不好意思,我离开一下\N- 没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.95,0:34:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了件重要的托付物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.87,0:34:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在哪儿可以找到你父亲呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:10.08,0:34:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.66,0:34:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我给你引见一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.29,0:34:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“洪都拉斯”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.87,0:34:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有“尼加拉瓜”,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.45,0:34:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.75,0:34:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就对了,它是脏的\N一种易腐烂的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.16,0:34:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 天堂鸟\N- 还有更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.00,0:34:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比利时母鸡最适合孵化它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.37,0:34:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者你可以亲自孵化它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.62,0:34:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想我可以看到你父亲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.87,0:34:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.08,0:34:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不觉得他举止怪异吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.20,0:35:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在示威呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.87,0:35:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.08,0:35:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意下面这些:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.12,0:35:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心胸狭窄,卖弄学问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.00,0:35:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有愚钝委琐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.91,0:35:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从未注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.29,0:36:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燕子从某些书的字里行间飞起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.25,0:36:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖燕子的所有诗章?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.87,0:36:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人人应当研究这些鸟的飞翔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:10.79,0:36:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,听我说\N我找到原始资料了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.70,0:36:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 原始资料?\N- 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.04,0:36:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.50,0:36:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无价值的垃圾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.08,0:36:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,书...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.29,0:36:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的孩子,这只是一个神话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.70,0:36:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们小时候相信的神话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.20,0:36:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们长大了,就不再相信它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.33,0:36:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上,许多书籍只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.83,0:36:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以提供给借来的生命使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.79,0:36:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们中的都只有一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:48.33,0:36:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在它翱翔时的瞬间理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.50,0:36:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像凤凰般鸣叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.54,0:36:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的所有书页像火一样通红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.33,0:36:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.91,0:37:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那唯一的瞬间\N我们从此以后一直爱它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.70,0:37:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管它们很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.50,0:37:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就要化作灰烬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:20.33,0:37:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对为什么没有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:23.70,0:37:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我们提供来自哈氏山脉的\N金丝雀,而感到纳闷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.33,0:37:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“孩子,这本书是一个神话”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.95,0:37:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“像凤凰一般翱翔...”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:11.83,0:38:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海德拉巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.37,0:38:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危地马拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.62,0:38:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔斯马尼亚岛,圣多明哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.66,0:38:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塞拉利昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.20,0:38:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉布拉多,巴巴多斯\N特立尼达,萨尔瓦多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.41,0:38:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆罗洲\N苏门答腊,伯南布哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.25,0:38:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希普拉邦迪亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:36.12,0:38:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡说,你也只会说潘非布拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.91,0:38:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈雷里瓦...\N阿布拉卡达布拉(译注:西方的一种咒语)...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.83,0:38:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为什么觉得,以前似乎来过这儿呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.25,0:38:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.25,0:39:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道我们,实际上预先知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:02.66,0:39:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们生命中看到的每件景色吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.20,0:39:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何全新的事物...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.95,0:39:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾发生过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.00,0:39:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你理解我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.20,0:39:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们未曾预料到的事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:00.08,0:40:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.16,0:40:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它真的发生了,或是没有发生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.00,0:40:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是还是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:10.45,0:40:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些事情完全不会发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.00,0:40:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们太伟大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:16.66,0:40:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太伟大而不能适合做大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.83,0:40:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们仅仅是试着去发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.91,0:40:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,告诉我她是否真正存在过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.45,0:41:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她确实存在过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:07.50,0:41:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么可以破坏我的必然之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:07.66,0:42:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心,她听不到我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.58,0:42:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我逝去的母亲,她住在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:16.50,0:42:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是鬼魂和幽灵附体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.79,0:42:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幼虫和蝶蛹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.95,0:42:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她同它们一起入睡\N把它们一起带入梦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.83,0:42:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,清晨,睡眼朦胧地醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.87,0:42:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么也不记得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.20,0:42:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为她得自食其力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.29,0:42:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是她为什么那么悲伤的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.12,0:42:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道“时间不能改变”那个故事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.79,0:42:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那些所有故事中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.33,0:42:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一个你没有听过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.20,0:42:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在很久以前,夜晚被收回去的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.50,0:43:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有足够的耐心听它吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.66,0:43:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人会在天空中行走...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.79,0:43:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经常在路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.50,0:43:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这人是一个永久的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:14.37,0:43:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他将经过我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:17.12,0:43:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走过长长的阶梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.70,0:43:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个故事总是会发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:23.25,0:43:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一遍一遍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.54,0:43:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.95,0:43:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你依靠我吧,碧安卡\N直到我流尽最后一滴血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.29,0:43:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.75,0:43:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.95,0:43:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她长得什么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.33,0:43:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她全身灰白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:57.04,0:44:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,触碰她手的话\N必会有难以名状的兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.54,0:44:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你在那儿看到了什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.25,0:44:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是五彩斑斓的,光芒四射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.08,0:44:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绑架,追击,背叛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.41,0:44:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个关于公主被劫持和被改变的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.20,0:44:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夸张和虚构
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:24.95,0:44:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爪哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.08,0:44:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苏门答腊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.00,0:44:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆罗洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:31.04,0:44:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你愿意的话\N我建议你做一名统治者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.54,0:44:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然是化名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:36.50,0:44:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同邮票簿一起\N我们组成一个三人执政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:39.75,0:44:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这件不可理解的\N事件的主题寄托于其上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:45.20,0:44:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同邮票簿一起?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.70,0:44:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多么幼稚的问题!\N这是一本众所周知的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.87,0:44:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一本手册
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.75,0:44:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一本所有人类知识的手册
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:57.37,0:45:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是为什么故事会被传播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:01.16,0:45:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带着锐气,带着圆点和叹息被传播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.45,0:45:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但它需要一些精明和想象力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.70,0:45:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的话正变得胡言乱语和荒谬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:13.00,0:45:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为邮票簿的主人\N我仍有一些对你关心的残念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:17.95,0:45:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你嫉妒情感的爆发\N把我置于你的对立面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:23.08,0:45:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别忘了,是你依赖我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:29.54,0:45:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得去对面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.12,0:45:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她父亲是一个小船修理员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.20,0:45:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蒸汽船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:54.16,0:45:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侧面有轮子的那种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.45,0:45:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他每晚在码头等她,所有的灯都灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.33,0:46:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别去那儿,我有不祥之感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:03.00,0:46:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心,虽然我看起来好像很兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.58,0:46:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我也是很担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.37,0:46:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粗略翻阅邮票簿不是更安全吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.45,0:46:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那儿,你没看见我的新墨西哥州
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:15.08,0:46:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要的事情是要记住\N最后,是没有墨西哥州的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:18.45,0:46:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个墨西哥州都藏在他们的另一面里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:05.79,0:49:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的死只是表面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.29,0:49:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的呼吸是微弱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:11.79,0:49:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些生物不会是小说中的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:17.83,0:49:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只是临时的\N是为了一个大典被制造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:22.37,0:49:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他们着魔时\N在他们神经错乱时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:26.79,0:49:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们被当场抓获
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:29.16,0:49:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们被抓,这件事成为了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.45,0:49:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:36.62,0:49:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说,在人体模特的雕像里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:40.45,0:49:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个新的人产生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:44.83,0:49:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无政府主义者卢克尼\N伊丽莎白女皇的刺杀者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:03.70,0:50:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边的是德拉格\N塞尔维亚的恶魔女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:09.08,0:50:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那边是爱迪生和俾斯麦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.95,0:50:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皮裹腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:15.62,0:50:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是个一少年天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:18.41,0:50:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他家族的骄傲和希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:21.12,0:50:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他因手淫上瘾而毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:24.20,0:50:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸的是,他们不是真实的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.70,0:50:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们在他们的演出上\N已经投入了大量的精力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:34.62,0:50:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们显得苍白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:39.16,0:50:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带着疾病发烧引起的红晕而死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:46.54,0:50:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在请看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:48.66,0:50:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗朗兹·约瑟夫皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:52.95,0:50:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他的脸上是某种创新的组合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:56.50,0:51:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他一种笑的表情,他就能笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.16,0:51:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放大,这个微笑是没有掩饰的\N像一个痛苦的鬼脸和平常的坦率一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:05.29,0:51:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有个和他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:07.25,0:51:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不同思想和气质的小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:10.66,0:51:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他令人遗憾的对立者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:13.54,0:51:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一个令人讨厌的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.87,0:51:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马克西米利安大公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:22.37,0:51:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皇帝爱他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:25.33,0:51:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他却秘密地策划推翻皇帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:28.20,0:51:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先,他任命他为指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.95,0:51:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望他能解除痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:35.12,0:51:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他不久就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:39.04,0:51:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与拿破仑三世缔结了秘密联盟...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.62,0:51:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(这就是)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:46.12,0:51:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他用欺诈手段与他打成了平局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:49.58,0:51:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从而加入了墨西哥人的冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:51.83,0:51:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个年轻人,满脑子的空想与幻想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:54.91,0:51:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放弃了哈布斯堡继承人的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:57.16,0:52:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坠入到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:00.54,0:52:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法国“勒熙德”平飞球的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:08.16,0:52:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据其中一个版本\N他只是个君主的表亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:13.04,0:52:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据另一个版本;\N他从来就没出生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:16.50,0:52:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仅仅是通过皇帝的恐惧和胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:19.75,0:52:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被造出的假想物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:22.45,0:52:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有个大问题就是\N把他一起放回原处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:26.04,0:52:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要掩饰他的伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:29.66,0:52:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤口是在韦拉·克鲁斯\N被处死时留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:32.83,0:52:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸的是,他更遭受健忘之苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:36.54,0:52:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得再次教会他的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:39.58,0:52:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我只能顺利地使他做出反应...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:43.04,0:52:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弗朗兹·约瑟夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:50.91,0:52:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他伸手去拿他的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:59.41,0:53:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他甚至伤害了维克多·伊曼纽尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:04.37,0:53:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时,他躲避得不够迅速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.00,0:53:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碧安卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:20.20,0:53:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和马克西米利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.08,0:53:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它仅仅纯粹是机械把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.29,0:53:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,适当的紧张,他行动起来\N就像他活着时那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:31.29,0:54:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纯粹是机械把戏,该死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:35.25,0:54:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热带地区的愤世嫉俗者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.37,0:54:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,热带地区的愤世嫉俗者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:40.75,0:54:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鲁道夫说,我是在夸大其词和捏造...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.62,0:54:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们本应当是在床上,服用他们的药的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.50,0:54:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不该被放在\N令人不舒服的雕像座上到这么晚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.41,0:55:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能闻到箭毒的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.16,0:55:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你愿意看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:06.37,0:55:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的武器收藏吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:09.00,0:55:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的,我的直觉\N没有把我引上邪路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:12.08,0:55:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这儿,处于表面的合法性之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:15.04,0:55:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事物能使人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:18.95,0:55:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁是真正的碧安卡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:27.58,0:55:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的妈妈是一个克里奥耳女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:29.75,0:55:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马克西米利安大公管她叫康奇塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:32.95,0:55:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那个名字她通过后门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:36.79,0:55:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走进了历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.95,0:55:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是她的外公?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:41.87,0:55:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,是母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:44.00,0:55:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马克西米利安倒台以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.87,0:55:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,康奇塔带着她的小女儿来到了巴黎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.62,0:55:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那儿她靠着寡妇抚恤金过活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:51.95,0:55:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那儿,历史失去了\N那个感人的人物的踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:55.62,0:55:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:57.54,0:56:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来为你完成它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:00.70,0:56:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些事情是机密的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:03.29,0:56:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好小心并克制你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:17.00,0:56:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,100,000比索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:21.29,0:56:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的份内事没有做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:24.00,0:56:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,这是一个多么昂贵的冒险事业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:28.41,0:56:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1900年,一个叫恩德·V...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:32.37,0:56:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外国的美少妇和她的\N女儿及丈夫离开了法国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:37.00,0:56:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持假护照来到澳大利亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:40.29,0:56:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在萨尔茨堡,换乘火车去维也纳时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:44.25,0:56:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全家被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:46.54,0:56:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得注意的是,德· V先生被释放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:51.12,0:56:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他却没有设法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:54.25,0:56:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他的妻子和女儿也被释放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:56.25,0:56:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他回到法国,消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:00.79,0:57:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个发现将属于我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.95,0:57:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会成功地识别那个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:14.12,0:57:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,150,000比索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:18.20,0:57:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真够麻烦的,你到底想要什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:22.33,0:57:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如你明白了新形势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:25.87,0:57:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你的决心就会告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:27.70,0:57:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我需要事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.45,0:57:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:37.91,0:57:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想,碧安卡的出身会被证明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:07.83,1:00:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑人,成群的黑人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:10.58,1:00:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每年这个时候,他们是从哪儿来呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:13.00,1:00:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气压一定很低...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.12,1:00:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碧安卡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:20.87,1:00:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本想你永远不会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:23.75,1:00:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:25.87,1:00:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:27.83,1:00:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要让好运常与我相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:30.95,1:00:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要完成我的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.45,1:00:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你给我带来可读的东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.95,1:00:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将要颁布的政令
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.66,1:00:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雏菊,雏菊,告诉我答案,快...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:52.62,1:00:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有风琴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:59.58,1:01:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技术的奇迹,它们会\N让它变得得心应手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:06.50,1:01:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在最伟大君主的王朝事务\N方面,我走得太远了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.37,1:01:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这些事务上,我变得如此地混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:14.66,1:01:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可能有麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:16.58,1:01:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备些密告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:18.66,1:01:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 密告?真的?\N- 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:21.62,1:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则你还想让事情,变得更好些吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:26.00,1:01:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:31.25,1:01:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去探究邪恶的深度\N消灭自身的意识...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:35.91,1:01:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一定是一种美妙的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:41.20,1:01:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想象一下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:42.79,1:01:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想变得...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:47.25,1:01:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,片刻地如此肮脏和可憎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:51.33,1:01:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你不想焕然一新吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.75,1:01:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动吧!行动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:56.75,1:01:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你将是他们中的一员...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:00.25,1:02:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑人的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:02.54,1:02:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在,在这关键时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.79,1:02:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你引诱我去告密
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.45,1:02:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连同你的愚忠和传教士的热诚\N你是滑稽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:15.33,1:02:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是我选择了鲁道夫又会怎么样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:17.91,1:02:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜欢他胜过你\N你是个令人生厌的学究
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.41,1:02:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定会顺从的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:25.79,1:02:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我去进行犯罪活动\N去进行自我毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:30.37,1:02:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鲁道夫,他会顺从你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:32.70,1:02:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你记得朗佳吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:35.66,1:02:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小时候和她一起玩过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.79,1:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朗佳,就是我\N我那时候是个男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:42.66,1:02:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候你喜欢我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.37,1:02:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碧安卡 碧安卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:46.33,1:02:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得事情越来越乱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:49.58,1:02:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定也要让我失望吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:51.25,1:02:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请出示车票
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.83,1:03:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,列车员
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:02.70,1:03:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里怎么了,是因为仁慈的缘故吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.83,1:03:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷静点,不要惊慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:10.54,1:03:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我们自己的证明信的期限之内\N我们可以解决这件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:15.04,1:03:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常的事实都会在\N规定的时间内安排好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:18.87,1:03:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使其走上正轨
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:22.75,1:03:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犹如沿着一条线一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:25.37,1:03:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这对于任何叙述和代替都是重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:29.12,1:03:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不错,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:32.87,1:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于这些事件,要做些什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:36.75,1:03:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些事件不能被及时的合理处置
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:39.20,1:03:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情发生的太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:42.54,1:03:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为所有的时间都被分配完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:46.62,1:03:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间范围是不是太小\N而不能完成所有的事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:50.75,1:03:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时间支线。有点不合法和可疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.83,1:03:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但当处理事情时\N那是不会被记录的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.83,1:04:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们不必那样大惊小怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:03.25,1:04:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许即使在现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:05.91,1:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们提起它时,也没必要惊慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:10.00,1:04:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个可疑的行动一直追随着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.04,1:04:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正走进了死胡同
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:20.29,1:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但一个人怎么能逃出这里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:24.66,1:04:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以试试再钻到床底下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:32.41,1:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起,我得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.29,1:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懦夫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:36.50,1:04:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望再回到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:45.16,1:04:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懦夫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.79,1:05:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.25,1:05:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看上去不太好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:44.70,1:05:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都混乱了,父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:51.50,1:05:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这个混乱之中\N人们要有极大的耐心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:56.37,1:05:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去寻找正确的含义
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:57.83,1:06:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通过仔细的语法分析就可以实现它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:02.45,1:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是非常有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:05.54,1:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,词组和语法...\N我, 你, 他, 我们, 你们, 他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:13.20,1:06:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,我记住了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:26.58,1:06:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去给人们找点时间...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:28.91,1:06:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人必须穿越鸟的鸣叫声,去消除诱惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:34.58,1:06:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们被标明是副词和介词
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:40.12,1:06:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是怯懦的代词
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:42.25,1:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢地使自己有一点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:45.75,1:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点完整的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.62,1:07:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传奇故事书...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:18.54,1:07:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从未被写过的书...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:21.79,1:07:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恢弘的史诗。。。\N苍白和使人厌倦的史诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:25.50,1:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有书名的小说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:28.37,1:07:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无脸的巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:31.08,1:07:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑暗的正文写给晚间乌云的戏剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:35.83,1:07:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游荡和迷失的书本...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:39.70,1:07:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有教区的主教里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:44.50,1:08:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近你有那么多工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:46.91,1:08:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我见你的灯在深夜里亮着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:51.33,1:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,试一下,或许你也能做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.00,1:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美极了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.37,1:09:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我曾经见过最漂亮的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.08,1:09:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记住,他叫大极乐鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:23.25,1:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或着叫天堂之鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:27.50,1:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主红雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:32.29,1:09:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红腹锦鸡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:35.87,1:09:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴胜(译注:鸟名)
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:41.58,1:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想让你带些东西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:46.54,1:09:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何,对一些事情要保留意见...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.08,1:09:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使它在你的血液里流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:52.70,1:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使它成为你生命中的一部分,保留它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:56.04,1:09:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与它一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:05.29,1:10:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进来,进来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:10.87,1:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,他们在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:13.16,1:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想让他们打扰我,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:21.04,1:11:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:24.91,1:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身都是蜘蛛网
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:28.08,1:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的外套被扯破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:31.20,1:11:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又去阁楼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.08,1:11:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店员们是贼,弄得我们卖东西只好赊账
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:46.62,1:11:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不关心这事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:49.66,1:11:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那个拿到商店去,你爸爸一定饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:08.08,1:12:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去商店!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:16.50,1:13:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在找你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.54,1:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真热
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:21.50,1:13:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁找我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.38,1:13:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,商店员工们,特别是提奥多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.67,1:13:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们会再爬梯子的,上上下下地爬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:59.75,1:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢,约瑟夫!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:04.25,1:14:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真希望你早点出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:21.34,1:14:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:23.75,1:14:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他们看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:39.29,1:14:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他们看看,吓一下他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:44.67,1:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜荷罗孚尼是个男人\N(基督教《次经》故事人物)
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:48.75,1:14:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把她保存在罗宋汤里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:51.88,1:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样她就看起来会很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:10.42,1:15:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要买她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:16.29,1:15:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是出售的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:18.63,1:15:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这个人头是在商店里\N那它就是来出售的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:23.38,1:15:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要买它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:01.13,1:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:04.42,1:16:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它拿走,这儿没地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:11.67,1:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要烦我,我太忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:28.46,1:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,商人贾科布
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:03.38,1:17:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:50.13,1:17:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒醒,约瑟夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:52.96,1:17:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你累了\N但那仅是更多几级台阶而已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:57.59,1:18:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你病了,你不好好照顾你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:02.25,1:18:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他来了,你听到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:06.46,1:18:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从儿提时
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:08.25,1:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就和他非常熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:10.42,1:18:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得他在学校时...\N那个自私的家伙使我作呕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:14.59,1:18:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狼吞虎咽地吃着\N很多涂了奶油的面包圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:19.50,1:18:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去见他一下,这样\N他就不认为我不理会他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:20.17,1:19:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我没弄错的话\N这就是贾科布的儿子,约瑟夫吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:24.34,1:19:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你头顶的天空,永远是蓝色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:27.96,1:19:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你脚下的大地,永远被露水湿润
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:30.67,1:19:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不需要说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:34.79,1:19:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能听到他们像蜂窝一样嗡嗡作响
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:39.67,1:19:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这仅是骗人的把戏\N可悲的使人困惑之物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:44.71,1:19:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母亲抱怨人们买东西只是赊账
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:47.84,1:19:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 他说什么?\N- 赊帐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:51.09,1:19:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定是理解错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:52.88,1:19:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以赊账方式卖东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:56.17,1:19:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再不想听到那句话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:58.79,1:20:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么一直弓着身子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:01.38,1:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你听我们说\N听这些智慧的人说吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:06.92,1:20:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的心献给我的知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:10.09,1:20:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只用现金交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:14.17,1:20:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们该帮助别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:15.92,1:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且要谨慎地避免...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:17.75,1:20:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使我们堕落
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:36.67,1:20:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的土地将享受七年的事业兴旺
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:41.79,1:20:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是塞伯尔,基督教徒\N如果我没错,他的儿子们是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:46.75,1:20:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纺纱工人和手工织布工
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:49.17,1:20:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,富人工作,是为了聚集财富...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:53.75,1:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息时都被他的财富包围着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:00.21,1:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穷人工作,是为了寻找食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:05.71,1:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最终变成一名乞丐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:29.96,1:25:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:02.96,1:26:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她停下了,不来公园了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:05.50,1:26:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们闻起来就是危险分子\N他们必须要监视着她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.96,1:26:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是一个彻底的谎言!\N外星人。马克西米利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:14.84,1:26:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,墨西哥,殖民地。停下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:18.42,1:26:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是谁告诉你的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:21.88,1:26:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,档案显示,那个阴谋从未被赦免过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:25.79,1:26:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟,我是邮票簿的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:30.38,1:26:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不再借给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:33.67,1:26:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须承认这个故事看起来\N是不可能的,甚至是不可信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.13,1:26:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为呢,鲁道夫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:42.92,1:26:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想出那邪恶的点子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.63,1:26:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超出所有可想象得到的幻想\N是谁的主意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:56.29,1:26:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己都很惊奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:02.67,1:27:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合作结束!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.75,1:27:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要设法不用你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.42,1:27:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白把那件事证明给我自己\N是完全正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:36.00,1:27:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德·V先生在哪儿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:37.59,1:27:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:40.54,1:27:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要看看事实是否如此\N公主在哪儿呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.54,1:27:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主殿下也离开了,他们都走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:49.50,1:27:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有疑问了,滚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:59.63,1:28:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有人出卖了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:55.17,1:28:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马,先生们,快上马
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:18.34,1:30:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生们,我给你们带来了\N不必要的麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:22.67,1:30:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些人自由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:25.67,1:30:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以自由地,不受干扰地行动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.21,1:30:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我失明时\N我明白要对课本做出注释...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:32.50,1:30:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为上帝意愿的解释者
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:34.67,1:30:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我错误的信仰里\N我曾控告过证据不足之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.42,1:30:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并且把他联系到某人身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:42.34,1:30:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,允许我吧,我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:44.17,1:30:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高贵的绅士们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:46.75,1:30:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有你,公主!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:48.59,1:30:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要放弃摄政,支持鲁道夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:51.29,1:30:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我将彻底地放弃权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.92,1:31:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们自由了,先生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.46,1:31:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以我们的信念之名...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:05.17,1:31:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我们被废黜的信念之名谢谢你们...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:10.04,1:31:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那将,不顾一切...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:14.79,1:31:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快一点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:16.92,1:31:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:28.88,1:31:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲!父亲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:31.54,1:31:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫加里波第过来,他是个\N老手,懂得治疗各种创伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:35.63,1:31:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碧安卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:41.29,1:31:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿担架来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:43.25,1:31:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点!担架!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:51.09,1:31:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今夜真是命中注定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:54.13,1:31:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我没有预见的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:56.09,1:31:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实际上,一颗高贵的心\N在他的胸膛里跳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:59.84,1:32:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我冤枉了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:02.79,1:32:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鲁道夫,你的职责是去安慰碧安卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:05.29,1:32:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去加强你对的爱,以此代替她的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:13.38,1:32:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:15.17,1:32:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你将毫无疑问想带他走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:18.63,1:32:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们组织成一列
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:20.92,1:32:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站成一列!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:24.17,1:32:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站成一列!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:03.17,1:33:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有一件事儿,鲁道夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:04.96,1:33:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赡养这些在他们年老时\N无家可归的英雄们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:08.92,1:33:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应当是我的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:11.75,1:33:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不幸的是,我是个穷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:18.88,1:33:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:20.17,1:33:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,10,000
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:25.92,1:33:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 5,000?\N- 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.34,1:33:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,12,000
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:52.59,1:33:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生们,这件事发生之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:56.21,1:33:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在任何蜡像馆都不会\N有布告牌承认你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:58.63,1:34:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你们没有实践的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.17,1:34:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朋友提供了\N一个可供购买的捐赠
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.09,1:34:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它就是12桶的风琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:09.00,1:34:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们将为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:11.09,1:34:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的人民演奏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:14.21,1:34:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给他们带来欢乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:18.09,1:34:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:19.75,1:34:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲爱的朋友们,高贵的绅士们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:23.92,1:34:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与我一起祝愿,为最近结婚者们祝愿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:26.75,1:34:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新婚夫妇万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:40.34,1:34:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生们,再见!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:42.92,1:34:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留心那些你们将在那里看到的警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:48.09,1:34:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永远不要试图猜测...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:51.54,1:34:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神的介入
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:55.13,1:34:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类永远是无知的,先生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:58.96,1:35:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类永远是无知的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:06.13,1:35:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是约瑟夫,贾科布的儿子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:10.38,1:35:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:11.46,1:35:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你,以前是不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:14.84,1:35:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做过《圣经》中\N约瑟夫曾做过的普通梦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:17.42,1:35:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:24.17,1:35:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道那个梦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:28.46,1:35:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在最高处曾被严厉地批判过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:30.92,1:35:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我拒绝回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:33.13,1:35:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:35.25,1:35:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以皇帝陛下的名义,你被捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:41.13,1:35:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任你处置
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:46.42,1:35:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,皇帝陛下的繁文缛节真罗嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:51.25,1:35:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我胜过了那个早先的梦\N而与更严肃的行为一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:55.88,1:35:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用自杀来进行赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:59.42,1:36:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞成这个过时的梦\N将会挽救我的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:22.54,1:36:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:24.17,1:36:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我偏头疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:28.75,1:36:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧,我想喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:40.00,1:36:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿黛拉在家吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:42.13,1:36:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她去了美国
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:46.25,1:36:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:48.96,1:36:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她坐船去的?船沉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:52.04,1:36:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无人生还
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:54.79,1:36:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那时起,她就杳无音讯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:58.17,1:36:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那父亲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:00.59,1:37:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在哪儿呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:04.38,1:37:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他离开了很多次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:06.67,1:37:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但每次都会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:11.79,1:37:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有自己的优势
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:15.34,1:37:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已经为他的最后离去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:18.42,1:37:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:43.04,1:37:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带我去见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:46.92,1:37:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:51.59,1:37:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想,你该见他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:03.96,1:38:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,商店也没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:06.25,1:38:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有时候仍去那儿\N卖点儿剩余的东西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:12.00,1:38:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是一定要保持百叶窗半关着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:05.38,1:39:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是那些男人中的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:10.29,1:39:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...在他那睡熟的脸之上\N上帝伸出了他的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:14.67,1:39:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样他们就知道...\N他们所不知的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:19.75,1:39:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们变得投机...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:24.00,1:39:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和多疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:27.96,1:39:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他们紧闭的双眼下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:32.42,1:39:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遥远国土的影像...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:37.42,1:39:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放映过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:02.84,1:40:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类将走进永世的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:08.46,1:40:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们将哭,在街道上游荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:13.09,1:40:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到银索断开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:17.29,1:40:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,金丝带缩短
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:21.96,1:40:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水桶在水上碎裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:26.34,1:40:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水井的辘轳裂开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:30.00,1:40:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尘归尘,土归土
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:09.88,1:41:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你来了,我真高兴,约瑟夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:13.63,1:41:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人吃惊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:16.79,1:41:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这儿,我是如此地孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:19.71,1:41:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不该抱怨我的处境
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:23.71,1:41:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经经过更糟的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:29.38,1:41:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须告诉你点儿事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:39.38,1:41:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是,你不许笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:39.38,1:41:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经在这儿租赁了商店场地
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:43.75,1:41:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再想象任何辉煌的事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:49.46,1:41:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家的话,我会因这个摊位而害羞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:53.00,1:41:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在这儿,我们不得不放弃...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:57.00,1:41:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们更多的尊严\N你不同意吗,约瑟夫?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:02.79,1:42:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样,人总是会去设法生存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:10.29,1:42:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定是把发条弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:17.21,1:42:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:19.79,1:42:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就接着睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:23.71,1:42:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不会想象得到\N收回欠账是多么地困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:29.42,1:42:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这儿的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:31.63,1:42:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是如此地不信任老商人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:34.71,1:42:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有令人尊敬的过去的商人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:40.59,1:42:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还记得市场广场的眼镜店吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:45.92,1:42:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的商店恰好就在它的隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:50.34,1:42:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面也没有招牌,但你会找得到它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:01.04,1:43:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好穿件衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:03.42,1:43:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在行李箱里没找到\N他们忘记装上它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:09.96,1:43:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:50.09,1:47:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:53.84,1:47:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你病得很重,你不好好照顾自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:59.17,1:48:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别烦我,没看我忙着吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:25.88,1:48:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你一封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:28.67,1:48:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我桌子上的文件堆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:44.67,1:50:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想象一下,我第一天来这儿的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:47.17,1:50:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我饱餐了一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:51.25,1:50:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛肉蘑菇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:54.04,1:50:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那块该死的肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:57.04,1:51:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须警告你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:01.54,1:51:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他们要给你一块牛肉时\N你们一定要当心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:07.71,1:51:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那块
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:09.50,1:51:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛肉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:13.00,1:51:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍能感觉到我胃里有团火
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:18.04,1:51:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一趟一趟地去厕所...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:20.96,1:51:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我几乎不能应付它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:24.13,1:51:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来,比如说,一块烤肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:28.67,1:51:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上一小块奶油?\N还有肉汁,饱餐一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:34.96,1:51:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这儿,我们什么都不用做
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:39.92,1:51:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们能付得起\N像城里的一样好的盛宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:47.00,1:51:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使,百万人中的的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:54.38,1:51:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必须承认他是迷人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:03.00,1:52:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要蜡烛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:08.09,1:52:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至这里的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:10.75,1:52:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都以独特的方式戴着她们的丝带
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:13.67,1:52:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你只瞥其中一个女孩一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:16.13,1:52:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就会遇到那种性感的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:22.92,1:52:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种表情带着它那可爱的必然性
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:25.13,1:52:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会令我们感到激动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:15.67,1:53:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得马上见医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:20.21,1:53:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他刚好去了餐馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:24.42,1:53:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚才就在那儿呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:26.25,1:53:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的意思是说,他正在外科手术室
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:30.96,1:53:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们得承认,我们被困住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:37.50,1:53:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疗养院的管理部门
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:41.63,1:53:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有给我们带来麻烦\N甚至也没给我们合适的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:46.04,1:53:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只好用我们自己的设备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:48.79,1:53:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有床,更别提干净的床单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:01.00,1:54:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那谜一般和谨慎的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:05.38,1:54:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直是骗人的把戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:07.63,1:54:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有一个要打开所有门的强烈愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:11.92,1:54:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并想曝光那个,我们曾卷入过的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:16.71,1:54:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好睡一觉,你几乎站不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:29.13,1:55:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊哈,约瑟夫,约瑟夫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:33.25,1:55:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直躺在这儿,没人照料
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:37.13,1:55:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电话线被剪断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:41.21,1:55:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有人来看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:44.34,1:55:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有人甚至能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:48.46,1:55:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我端杯茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:02.46,1:56:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:06.88,1:56:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开了他正生病的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:09.75,1:56:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到镇子里追女孩去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:13.75,1:56:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约瑟夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:17.00,1:56:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应当常来商店啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:23.59,1:56:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,店员们在盗取我们的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:29.17,1:56:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个店要毁了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:34.25,1:56:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让它自我运行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:40.04,1:56:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看我的心脏跳得多么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:45.71,1:56:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要油尽灯枯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:04.09,1:57:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,约瑟夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:06.75,1:57:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那儿有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:09.13,1:57:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从家里寄来的邮件吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:55.25,1:57:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,医生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:56.42,1:57:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看起来不舒服,脱掉上衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:00.04,1:58:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我给你检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:02.75,1:58:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那激动的心态,是非常不可理喻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:04.42,1:58:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的身体尤其是你的神经系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:09.38,1:58:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得不去适应新的环境
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:20.09,1:58:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是个白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:22.59,1:58:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我使自己被带有\N迷惑性的广告所蒙蔽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:25.75,1:58:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而把我父亲送到这儿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:28.13,1:58:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“让时间返回去...”
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:32.25,1:58:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听起来不错\N但它实际上会到什么地步呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:37.25,1:58:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这儿,一个人能得到\N那时间的充分价值吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.00,1:58:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是被消耗掉的时间\N被其他人耗尽的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:46.50,1:58:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消耗了的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:48.71,1:58:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它是回溯的时间,二手的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:54.84,1:58:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你父亲的存在状态怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:58.50,1:59:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你都可以和他讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:02.96,1:59:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:06.17,1:59:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应当对医生感激不尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:09.46,1:59:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了,宇宙是人类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:13.71,1:59:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以在宇宙中四处飘荡,翻筋斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:16.34,1:59:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...从这颗星星跳到另一颗星星上\N但请你不要篡改时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:21.17,1:59:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要的问题就是快速地分解...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:33.25,1:59:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:39.34,1:59:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都知道“时间”
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:42.42,1:59:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个不服从命令份子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:46.00,1:59:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一定的范围内\N只保持它自己的不稳定性
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:52.84,1:59:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并对渐增的和严密的规则负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:01.25,2:00:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了脱离警戒,它开始恶作剧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:05.38,2:00:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:07.96,2:00:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该更好地照顾自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:11.29,2:00:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿得更暖和些
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:14.42,2:00:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始时
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:17.88,2:00:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你需要更多的练习\N然后我们将观察你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:23.25,2:00:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,振作起来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:35.79,2:00:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上,幸好父亲不再活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:41.50,2:00:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样,他就不能被真正地联系上


